			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Anaris, the key to the Necro strategy is FEAR and DARKNESS. It is easy to solo a critter if he is walking off with his back to you, your pet hits for max damage most of the time and when augmented often does over 100 dam a round. Lay down some DOTs and the game is over. <BR>
<BR>
A necro rarely gets hit when using FEAR. You rooting Earth Pet is gonna get his butt handed to him after a while if you cannot get your DDs on the MOB fast.<BR>
<BR>
All Giants are easy for a good necro. If Darkness and Fear stick, you will have one dead giant on your hands. If they don't stick, well, lets not try to think about that shall we ;)
				</font>
			</td>

